@node "Wymagania" "Ami Atlas v2.29 PL - Requirements"

Requirements

To run  Ami Atlas v2.29  you need  Amiga with  OS v2.04 or higher.  If you use
other version - check requirements in original manual.  I'm not guarantee good
work Ami Atlas with my polish locale in other wersion than 2.29.

@endnode

@node "Instalacja" "Ami Atlas v2.29 PL - installation"

Installation

To run Ami Atlas  with polish locale,  you must copy all  files including this
archive to  your Ami Atlas Drawer  (i.e. Work:AmiAtlas/).  Next ru n Ami Atlas
and change language in program's preferences.

@endnode

@node "Wordworth_Info" "Wordworth - informacja"

Information about Ami Atlas

Ami Atlas is very good  (it's not only my opinion) car atlas.  You may need it
if you want  travel to  other city  and you want know,  how do it i.e. fastest 
or less  expensive.  Ami Atlas  has more preferences,  if you wanna  know more
about Ami Atlas - look at program.  It's very configurable,  you may  use more
maps for this program, change it and create yours.

@endnode

